nds hiking in Marin or exploring new restaurants in the Mission.\n\nArjun feels deeply connected to San Francisco\u2019s unique current of intellectual energy and cultural vibrancy. While he has achieved the financial success his parents dreamed of for him, his aspirations are now more personal. He hopes to see Maya thrive in college and aims to eventually transition from his demanding corporate role to advising non-profit biotech firms, applying his hard-won expertise to causes with a more direct human impact."
